'From Squeak 2.5 of August 6, 1999 [latest update: #1514] on 4 October 1999 at 8:16:27 am'!"Change Set:		sysMenuTweak-swDate:			4 October 1999Author:			Scott WallacePromotes #addModelItemsToWindowMenu: to Object (from Model) because some system window models do not inherit from Model.  Thanks to Bert Freudenberg for pointing this out."!!Object methodsFor: 'user interface' stamp: 'sw 10/4/1999 08:13'!addModelItemsToWindowMenu: aMenu	"aMenu is being constructed to be presented to the user in response to the user's pressing on the menu widget in the title bar of a morphic window.  Here, the model is given the opportunity to add any model-specific items to the menu, whose default target is the SystemWindow itself."! !Model removeSelector: #addModelItemsToWindowMenu:!